header.name: mapone
header.description: This map is a simple map used in the GameManager tutorial. It provides simple scenerio and allows access to a custom game actor developed throughout the tutorial.

event.name: SpeedBoost
event.description: Give the tank a small speed boost (+5) - this boost can exceed the speed cap.

event.name: TestShaders
event.description: A test message to allow us to reset our shaders. Just example code for how to manipulate shaders.

event.name: ToggleEngine
event.description: Toggles the tank engine on and off.

event.name: TankFired
event.description: The tank fired a shot. The blimps listen for this and check to see if they are the current target. If so, they take damage, else they ignore.

event.name: ResetStuff
event.description: Sort of restarts the level. Blimps come back alive, the tank goes back to home position, and you can blow em all up again!
